WEBVTT

00:02:58.696 --> 00:03:00.070
I found this thing

00:03:00.094 --> 00:03:02.807
that connected my head to my heart

00:03:02.831 --> 00:03:04.831
and my hand to everything.

00:03:05.463 --> 00:03:08.066
I could see the world in new ways.

00:03:08.090 --> 00:03:09.979
I found connections in corners

00:03:10.003 --> 00:03:12.966
and the solutions to problems
I never knew existed.

00:03:12.990 --> 00:03:16.252
It's like the world with all its
positive and negative spaces

00:03:16.276 --> 00:03:17.915
could now be seen.

00:03:17.939 --> 00:03:19.371
And just by seeing it,

00:03:19.395 --> 00:03:21.283
there was no longer any fear.

00:03:21.307 --> 00:03:23.569
It's like my pen was a flashlight,

00:03:23.593 --> 00:03:26.053
and the unknown was still there,

00:03:26.077 --> 00:03:27.467
but it wasn't scary.

00:03:27.861 --> 00:03:31.926
After five years of living in Japan
and focusing on my craft,